title: Intro to Sherman and Pippin
body: This is an introduction to Andrew's two dogs, Sherman and Pippin.

title: Day 1 of Shelter In-Place
body: This is the best thing ever! I get to stay at home with the dogs alllllllll dayyyyyyy looonnnngggg. Woohoo!

title: Day 15 of Shelter In-Place
body: Pretty sure Sherman thinks I'm a dog.

title: Day 49 of Shelter In-Place
body: Pippin taught Monday's CSE 154 lecture and nobody noticed. Dog training is progressing nicely.
